<plot>Chris (Ken McDougall) is a dancer dying of AIDS. He has chosen euthanasia to end his suffering. With the assistance of his lover Val (Jack Nicholsen) and his doctor (Daniel MacIvor), he surrounds himself in his last hours with everything that made his life special and creates his ultimate work of art by choreograph ing his own death.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569863</url></doc>
